profile:
Canada's Restoration Services is a leader in the restoration industry with over 12 years of experience. We specialize in mold removal, asbestos testing and removal, water damage restoration, fire and smoke damage and reconstruction.

We operate 24/7 and guarantee to be on site within 45 minutes for all emergencies. We provide same day appointments and have completed over 10,000 inspections and jobs nationwide. We work with every insurance company across Canada to help make the process quicker and easier for you and your family. We also provide free financing for all eligible customers to help ease any burdens.

We are a nationwide company and have been awarded over 13 years running  by HomeStars as Top Restoration Company. We value our customers and work hard to provide professional and reliable services. Call and speak to an expert today! We service Ontario, Quebec, and Alberta!
service_area:
Our Certified Experienced Water Damage Specialists and Mold Inspectors are strategically located throughout the provinces.

This enables Emergency Response within 45 minutes or less.

profile:
First Image Demo Groups Inc.,  is a family owned and operated business specializing in all facets of demolition services. We pride ourselves on providing value to our community and the many satisfied customers we serve.

Our talented and experienced staff will work with you to provide the resources and insights required to properly handle your demolition requirements.

The Executive Team constantly strives to improve procedures, educates staff, develops better demolition methods and continually invests in state of the art equipment.

The Project Management and Estimating Team work closely with customers and provide the best and most cost effective solutions to address your project needs.

The Accounting Team helps and supports the entire organization and works closely with customers keeping them informed with job related details and information.

We are founded on a philosophy of integrity, work hard, work as team, and above all stand out as the true leader in demolition services.

We are Toronto’s Interior & Exterior Demolition Specialists and we invite you to see the difference.
